                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-235-victim2032 t18321129-235-viclabel1323"></join>. The prisoner had been my <rs id="t18321129-235-deflabel1324" type="occupation">errand-boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-235-defend2030 t18321129-235-deflabel1324"></join> for six or seven years; in consequence of the loss of some pigeons, I went to his father's residence on the 15th of November - he sent a young woman on Thursday morning to say he was not able to attend to his duty - I found at his father's, the whole of the property stated in the indictment, some of which has my private mark on it.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321129-235-person2034">
                  JOSEPH 
                  BEAL
               <interp inst="t18321129-235-person2034" type="surname" value="BEAL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321129-235-person2034" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
