                     <interp inst="t18321129-235-person2037" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a house-agent. I know the house the property was found in; I let it to the prisoner, and he paid the rent of the premises.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. Q. He had a good character? A. I believe he has.</p>
               <p>
